    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Budget Guardian: Health Realm </strong>combines engaging gameplay with educational elements, making complex financial concepts both accessible and enjoyable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/9e3a8c68ea6a9414bfd8ab74df730089.poster.avif?t=1752855533\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/9e3a8c68ea6a9414bfd8ab74df730089.webm?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/9e3a8c68ea6a9414bfd8ab74df730089.mp4?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the whimsical world of Hindmarchville, where the villagers have elected a cat as their mayor, leading to some peculiar occurrences. In this casual simulation adventure, you play as Aayto, a dedicated health professional who has come to town to establish a care centre. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/c8a42b881ee98b6c564f31f317dc5bfe.poster.avif?t=1752855533\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/c8a42b881ee98b6c564f31f317dc5bfe.webm?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/c8a42b881ee98b6c564f31f317dc5bfe.mp4?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, as you assist the villagers, you soon discover that their strange behaviour might be more than just small-town eccentricities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There will be challenges ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/1acb10ffefcd776578bda26c85c14d0f.poster.avif?t=1752855533\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/1acb10ffefcd776578bda26c85c14d0f.webm?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/1acb10ffefcd776578bda26c85c14d0f.mp4?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission? Unravel the mystery behind Hindmarchville’s odd happenings while managing the care centre’s finances. You’ll need to balance budgets, optimise resources, and make strategic decisions to keep the centre running smoothly—all while delving into the intricacies of healthcare finance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/d145f598cb4c6e98239851616f0ceabf.poster.avif?t=1752855533\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/d145f598cb4c6e98239851616f0ceabf.webm?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/d145f598cb4c6e98239851616f0ceabf.mp4?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you solve the village’s mystery and ensure the care centre prospers under the leadership of a feline mayor?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/9b0ab2a81a276c3d720acd08f0ae7b81.poster.avif?t=1752855533\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/9b0ab2a81a276c3d720acd08f0ae7b81.webm?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/9b0ab2a81a276c3d720acd08f0ae7b81.mp4?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a vaccine</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/a6e742649bdf36dc9eea23ef9025e400.poster.avif?t=1752855533\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/a6e742649bdf36dc9eea23ef9025e400.webm?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/a6e742649bdf36dc9eea23ef9025e400.mp4?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or make a potion (medicines)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/54d5e22f275a9e91247f37b0b2344d64.poster.avif?t=1752855533\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/54d5e22f275a9e91247f37b0b2344d64.webm?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/54d5e22f275a9e91247f37b0b2344d64.mp4?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play as a potential budget holder or just for fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/9a2de9b9c2f78f8258b761b85833e278.poster.avif?t=1752855533\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/9a2de9b9c2f78f8258b761b85833e278.webm?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278980/extras/9a2de9b9c2f78f8258b761b85833e278.mp4?t=1752855533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Aayto on his journey and welcome to Hindmarchville.</p>",
